title: Time Team - Season 07 (2000) - 12 Episodes
description:
Time Team - Season 07 (2000) - 12 Episodes

Season Summary:

Tony Robinson is back with regular experts Mick Aston, Phil Harding and Carenza Lewis for the first series of the millennium. Highlights include a visit to Hadrian's Wall and a search for King Offa's lost palace.


     Air Date     Title
01 02 Jan 2000 Denia, Spain - A Muslim port in Spain
02 09 Jan 2000 Cirencester, Gloucestershire - The mosaic at the bottom of the garden
03 16 Jan 2000 Wierre-Effroy, France - One of the first spitfires lost in France
04 23 Jan 2000 Waddon, Dorset - An Iron Age roundhouse and a henge
05 30 Jan 2000 Birdoswald, Cumbria - Hadrian's Wall
06 06 Feb 2000 Elveden, Suffolk - In search of the earliest traces of mankind
07 13 Feb 2000 Coventry, West Midlands - The missing cathedral and the diabetic prior
08 20 Feb 2000 Basing House, Hampshire - The royalists' last stand
09 27 Feb 2000 Flag Fenn, Cambridgeshire - A Bronze Age barrow and walkway
10 05 Mar 2000 Sutton, Hereford - In search of the palace of King Offa
11 12 Mar 2000 Greenwich, London - A Roman temple in sight of the Millenium Dome
12 19 Mar 2000 Hartlepool, Northumberland - Nuns in Northumbria
